### 14. KEY DIFFERENCES BETWEEN PLUGINS

| Feature | IRC | Nostr | Telegram |
|---------|-----|-------|----------|
| Chat Types | direct + group | direct only | direct + group |
| Media Support | true | false | true |
| Account Model | Multi-account (host:nick) | Single (private key) | Multi-account (token) |
| Auth | plaintext/TLS + NickServ | Private key | Bearer token |
| Streaming | blocked | allowed | allowed |
| Markdown | configurable | configurable | configurable |
| Complex Src | Medium (~35 files) | Small (~24 files) | Large (~192 files) |

